snippet.title: Diana turned into the Little Mermaid Princess
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma visited the Mermaid Boutique in Dubai. The Sea Fairies turned Diana into the Little Mermaid Princess. Diana dresses in the Little Mermaid costume, does makeup and hair style like Ariel Disney Princess.
